reviewText:
The rare Dramatics-Biggest Hits Live Concert is one of 5 live concerts including The Four Tops-40th Anniversary Special Live at the MGM Grand in Las Vegas, The Whispers-The Beat Goes On Live, The Intruders Review includes their hits,Cowboys To Girls and I'll Always Love My Mama and last but not least
is Cuba Gooding Sr.& The Main Ingredient/The Delfonics Live at B.B. King's. What a treat, if you like old school you will love this collection.
